name: FNF - Vs. Cartoon Cat
description:
After defeating monster, BF and GF realized that monster was scared and left the place as if he was running away from something, BF and GF were confused. The place turned black and white, and out of nowhere a cat that looked like a cartoon from the 30s showed up
This mod replaces monster

For the first one you have to press 7 and switch the song to monster, then reload the json
